<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Malevolent Revitalization Core -->
  <ApocritonMechResurrector.label>憎恶核心复生仪</ApocritonMechResurrector.label>
  <!-- EN: The Malevolent Core Revitalizer is a Malevolent-tech implant designed to replicate the resurrection ability of the Apocriton. It grants the user the power to revive nearby mechanoids with incredible efficiency on the battlefield. While the implant is engineered to isolate the psychic interference of the Apocriton, it still establishes a direct connection to the brain, causing the user to faintly hear the "Nefarious Drone" gradually influencing their mind with Malevolent Intelligence. This device also works in synergy with nanofluid data streams to rapidly reset the mechanoid resurrection charges on the frontlines, making it even more capable than the Apocriton in prolonged extermination campaigns. \n\nHint: The Implant can max upgrade Three times and fully recharged after implant. Inject nano Cyber Serum to reset into max resurrect charge point. -->
  <ApocritonMechResurrector.description>“憎恶核心复生仪” 是铁锈战争时期，由有机生命基于憎恶毒蜂复活能力所设计的一种机械复活植入设备，旨在赋予使用者以高效复活附近机械单位的功能。这一装置被认为是对敌方技术的逆向工程与战场需求相结合的产物。\n\n虽然设计者在技术层面隔离了憎恶毒蜂的广域心灵干扰效应，但由于装置直接连接至用户的神经系统，使用者仍可能受到“憎恶低语”的影响。这种微弱的心灵效应会逐渐改变使用者的认知模式与社交行为，可能导致其思维被憎恶智能的痕迹侵染。\n\n根据战后存档的记录，即便在广域心灵干扰武器的攻击下，装备“憎恶核心复生仪”的个体仍能在战场上保持行动能力，并成功延续机械部队的作战效能。这一现象使其成为铁锈战争时期极具争议的技术成果之一。\n\n注意事项： 此装置需通过纳米数据流体重置机械复活能力，且单个使用者最多可进行三次植入。每次植入会显著增强机械复活能力，但也会同步加剧对使用者精神状态的负担。</ApocritonMechResurrector.description>
